<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 22:06:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列公众应该受到指责，而不是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-public-is-to-blame-not-netanyahu/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6991b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-public-is-to-blame-not-netanyahu/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6991b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将无法逃脱指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wont-be-able-to-escape-blame/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6971b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wont-be-able-to-escape-blame/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6971b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登为何访问战时以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-3ef6-d2b8-a7db-feff186c0000</link><description>在明确谴责哈马斯恐怖活动后，美国总统拜登带着重要的政治和道德资本抵达以色列。但美以议程上仍存在敏感问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-3ef6-d2b8-a7db-feff186c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划撤离黎巴嫩边境附近社区，许多人拒绝离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-to-evacuate-communities-close-to-border-with-lebanon-many-refuse-to-leave/0000018b-3ef7-df22-a5eb-3fff57f10000</link><description>据《国土报》调查，居住在这些社区的 27,000 名居民中，约有 15,000 人仍留在家中。预计他们中的大多数人将很快被疏散，并被送往由以色列政府支付费用的酒店和宾馆</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-to-evacuate-communities-close-to-border-with-lebanon-many-refuse-to-leave/0000018b-3ef7-df22-a5eb-3fff57f10000</guid></item><item><title>消防员从 7,500 英里外接听以色列的紧急呼叫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-firefighters-answering-israels-emergency-call-from-7-500-miles-away/0000018b-3e66-d2b8-a7db-fe6fb67a0000</link><description>与美国志愿者一起度过一个下午，在以色列中部灭火和追赶火箭弹。目前驻扎在拉姆勒的一名加州消防员表示，“这与我在美国经历过的任何事情都不一样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-firefighters-answering-israels-emergency-call-from-7-500-miles-away/0000018b-3e66-d2b8-a7db-fe6fb67a0000</guid></item><item><title>“他写信给我：我的父母去世了，我需要帮助”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-17/ty-article-podcast/.premium/he-wrote-me-my-parents-are-dead-i-need-help/0000018b-3e82-d2b8-a7db-feef48080000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-17/ty-article-podcast/.premium/he-wrote-me-my-parents-are-dead-i-need-help/0000018b-3e82-d2b8-a7db-feef48080000</guid></item><item><title>让以色列在过度拥挤的条件下关押安全囚犯的法案获得初步批准</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-let-israel-hold-security-prisoners-in-overcrowded-conditions-gets-initial-approval/0000018b-3ed5-df22-a5eb-3ffd52930000</link><description>该法案将授权国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔免除居住空间要求，并让囚犯睡在地板上的床垫上</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 18:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-let-israel-hold-security-prisoners-in-overcrowded-conditions-gets-initial-approval/0000018b-3ed5-df22-a5eb-3ffd52930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称伊斯兰圣战组织火箭发射失败，导致加沙医院数百人死亡；哈马斯指责以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-on-gaza-city-hospital-gaza-health-ministry-says/0000018b-3ec5-dcae-afaf-7eff6ef70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡指责“野蛮的恐怖分子”对阿赫利医院的死亡负责。赫尔佐格猛烈抨击媒体对以色列的“血腥诽谤”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 18:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-on-gaza-city-hospital-gaza-health-ministry-says/0000018b-3ec5-dcae-afaf-7eff6ef70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医院拒绝治疗哈马斯恐怖分子，消息人士称“民族感情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hospital-refuses-to-treat-hamas-terrorist-sources-cite-national-feelings/0000018b-3e79-d2b8-a7db-fe7f7c320000</link><description>最近宣布的一项政策禁止公立医院治疗恐怖分子，但卫生部尚未公布明确的实施程序</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 17:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hospital-refuses-to-treat-hamas-terrorist-sources-cite-national-feelings/0000018b-3e79-d2b8-a7db-fe7f7c320000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对人质的家人感到恐惧。这可能会影响他的判断</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-petrified-of-the-hostages-families-it-could-impact-his-judgment/0000018b-3e01-d5be-a7eb-befd1bc50000</link><description>如果战争内阁中负责的成年人不保持警惕，以色列对哈马斯的军事反应将更多地是总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的政治算计的结果，而不是该国非常现实和紧迫的优先事项</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 15:48:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-petrified-of-the-hostages-families-it-could-impact-his-judgment/0000018b-3e01-d5be-a7eb-befd1bc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列柔道运动员雅埃尔·阿拉德加入国际奥委会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-judoka-yael-arad-joins-international-olympic-committee/0000018b-3e24-d2b8-a7db-fe6f191a0000</link><description>以色列国家奥委会主席阿拉德表示，国际奥委会投票承认她在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件后具有了新的意义</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 15:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-judoka-yael-arad-joins-international-olympic-committee/0000018b-3e24-d2b8-a7db-fe6f191a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在吊销数百名加沙劳工的工作许可证后拘留了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-detained-hundreds-of-gazan-laborers-after-revoking-their-work-permits/0000018b-3dbb-d582-a3cb-7dbb3dae0000</link><description>人权组织声称，政府没有拘留加沙人的法律权力，军队表示，由于战争，他们无法返回加沙，目前被拘留在约旦河西岸的一处设施中，问题仍在继续。接受检查</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-detained-hundreds-of-gazan-laborers-after-revoking-their-work-permits/0000018b-3dbb-d582-a3cb-7dbb3dae0000</guid></item><item><title>议会国家安全委员会批准新的、宽松的枪支许可证条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/knesset-national-security-committee-approves-new-lenient-fire-arms-license-conditions/0000018b-3db7-d5be-a7eb-bfff87090000</link><description>新规定本应是临时性的，但已被定为永久性的。司法部代表：尚未审查对自杀、家庭暴力和性别相关暴力的影响</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:39:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/knesset-national-security-committee-approves-new-lenient-fire-arms-license-conditions/0000018b-3db7-d5be-a7eb-bfff87090000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣押的法裔以色列人质的母亲：“乞求全世界带我的孩子回家”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-french-israeli-hostage-by-hamas-begging-the-world-to-bring-my-baby-home/0000018b-3d20-d101-a9ab-bf3c37aa0000</link><description>21 岁的玛雅·谢姆 (Maya Schem) 拥有法国和以色列双重国籍，在哈马斯袭击加沙边境附近的以色列社区时被哈马斯抓走。她的家人直到哈马斯在加沙发布她的视频几天后才发现她被扣为人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:48:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-french-israeli-hostage-by-hamas-begging-the-world-to-bring-my-baby-home/0000018b-3d20-d101-a9ab-bf3c37aa0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太白宫官员在访问以色列之前赞扬拜登：“这就是他”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/jewish-white-house-officials-applaud-biden-ahead-of-israel-visit-this-is-who-he-is/0000018b-3d41-d450-a3af-7d5d3f590000</link><description>一名高级工作人员表示，“现在有两件事给了我力量：犹太人民的韧性以及拜登总统的领导力和道德清晰度”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/jewish-white-house-officials-applaud-biden-ahead-of-israel-visit-this-is-who-he-is/0000018b-3d41-d450-a3af-7d5d3f590000</guid></item><item><title>考古、圣经机构谴责哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-17/ty-article/archaeological-biblical-institutions-condemn-hamas-massacre/0000018b-3d42-d101-a9ab-bf7e03f60000</link><description>以色列考古学家抱怨一周以来他们的沉默，美国海外研究协会周一谴责哈马斯对以色列平民的“恶毒屠杀”，而圣经文学协会则对世界反犹太主义抬头表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:15:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-17/ty-article/archaeological-biblical-institutions-condemn-hamas-massacre/0000018b-3d42-d101-a9ab-bf7e03f60000</guid></item><item><title>BBC记者因赞扬哈马斯袭击以色列平民而被停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bbc-reporters-suspended-for-praising-hamas-attacks-on-israeli-civilians/0000018b-3d75-d450-a3af-7d7d8cf80000</link><description>据报道，英国广播公司 (BBC) 旗下频道的一名记者点赞了一些推文，称针对以色列平民的屠杀是“一次高质量的行动”和“一个令人自豪的场景”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:54:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bbc-reporters-suspended-for-praising-hamas-attacks-on-israeli-civilians/0000018b-3d75-d450-a3af-7d7d8cf80000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争以来，澳大利亚犹太社区的宗教间关系紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/australian-jewish-communitys-interfaith-relations-strained-since-gaza-war/0000018b-3d14-d101-a9ab-bf3cff230000</link><description>至少两名拉比从澳大利亚犹太穆斯林基督教协会辞职，墨尔本地区犹太社区理事会正在考虑暂停跨宗教接触</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/australian-jewish-communitys-interfaith-relations-strained-since-gaza-war/0000018b-3d14-d101-a9ab-bf3cff230000</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨访问以色列，德国的特殊承诺面临最终考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-scholz-visits-israel-germanys-special-commitment-faces-the-ultimate-test/0000018b-3d23-d07d-a99b-fde3c12f0000</link><description>现在，德国比以往任何时候都更有历史责任积极、坚定不移地保卫以色列，而不仅仅是口头上</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-scholz-visits-israel-germanys-special-commitment-faces-the-ultimate-test/0000018b-3d23-d07d-a99b-fde3c12f0000</guid></item><item><title>“战争爆发，血沸腾”：定居者迫使巴勒斯坦人离开西岸家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theres-war-blood-is-boiling-settlers-force-palestinians-out-their-homes-in-west-bank/0000018b-3d35-d5b8-a78b-fd756b2e0000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯战争期间，约旦河西岸的定居者暴力不断升级：约旦河谷一个村庄的巴勒斯坦居民表示，定居者给了他们五个小时的时间逃离家园</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theres-war-blood-is-boiling-settlers-force-palestinians-out-their-homes-in-west-bank/0000018b-3d35-d5b8-a78b-fd756b2e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>